text:
This might be a stupid question but how do I get to the source of the rich text module?

If I have something like this in my email:

`{% widget_block rich_text "email_body" overrideable=True, label="Email Body" %}
                {% widget_attribute "html" %}
                &lt;h2&gt;Here is a heading&lt;/h2&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;Here is some content.&lt;/p&gt;
                {% end_widget_attribute %}
                {% end_widget_block %}`
It wouldnt be as simple as just adding a width to widget correct?
